  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the association of Rheumatoid Arthritis (RA)-related
      antibodies and periodontal inflammation in subjects at-risk for Rheumatoid Arthritis.
      Subjects will undergo periodontal and joint examinations, as well as collection of body
      fluids to measure Rheumatoid Arthritis-related antibodies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
